headline: Vanguard Is Now the Top Investor in MicroStrategy Stock. Should You Buy MSTR Too?
summary: MSTR stock is up close to 4,000% in the last five years as the Bitcoin proxy continues to outperform the world’s largest cryptocurrency. Should you buy, sell, or hold MSTR stock today?
